    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Boreomysis californica Ortmann, 1894. Female (CL 10.21 mm; TL 18.73 mm) (ICML-EMU-12544-A). A, thoracopod 1 with magnification of distal articles (arrow); B, thoracopod 2 with magnification of distal articles (arrow); C, thoracopod 3; D, thoracopod 4." ;
