    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Boreomysis californica Ortmann, 1894. A‒E, male (CL 10.70 mm; TL 25.11 mm) (ICML-EMU-12554-A); F‒J, female (CL 10.21 mm; TL, 18.73 mm) (ICML-EMU-12554-A). A‒E, pleopods 1 to 5; F‒J, pleopods 1 to 5." ;
